com.ibm.team.build.ant.task

Class BuildResultRetrieverTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • Task
      • com.ibm.team.build.ant.task.AbstractTeamBuildTask
        • com.ibm.team.build.ant.task.AbstractRetrieverTask
          • com.ibm.team.build.ant.task.BuildResultRetrieverTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IStaticReset

    public class BuildResultRetrieverTask
extends AbstractRetrieverTask
    Ant task for setting Ant properties with values from a build result.

    Optional attributes are:

    • labelProperty - The ant property in which to store the label of the build result.
    • deleteAllowedProperty - The ant property in which to store the delete allowed value (true or false) of the build result.
    • tagsProperty - The ant property in which to store the tags of the build result.
    See AbstractRetrieverTask for additional required and optional attributes.
    Since:
    0.8.5
